# CAPSURE™ WITH FORMULA GUIDE

## Bundles the Global Color Reference with Handheld Color Measurement

Sku#: GP1609B

$ 1,084.00

Add To Cart

Own the gamut of Graphics & Fashion and Home + Interiors color libraries on one compact color measurement device, plus all 2,390 Pantone® Spot colors in this dynamic bundle. Use the innovative CAPSURE™ color matching tool to measure and match color on the spot from any surface, material, or fabric to your choice of Pantone Library. This versatile set makes it easy to accurately translate any color inspiration the user finds into an achievable color. The Pantone Formula Guide provides a universal reference for brand guidelines and spot color printing, ensuring consistency in projects like signage, packaging, logos and branding, marketing materials, and more. Elevate your workflow from inspiration through production with the CAPSURE™ with Formula Guide set.

